This is the final month of the year and I plan on ending it as strong as possible!  God has tremendously blessed me this past year and I can’t wait for 2024 to start so I can continue to build on everything he has bestowed upon me. 
Over the past few months I’ve been praying and asking for guidance on not only how to become better as a person, or in the gym, or in my career, but on also how to be a better servant to God. To be a vessel and to share how even at my lowest points Jesus is always there to pick you up and bless you beyond belief. A big thing that has hit me is figuring out ways to give back to others in honor of Him.  And that’s just one of many things I have in store for 2024! Can’t wait to share what else.
